<module>
    <h>fuirich</h>
    <p><g>fuirich</g>
        <en>wait, stay, live</en> is a <a href="?xx=verbs/simple_verbs">simple verb</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>nouns</h>
        <section>
            <h>locative</h>
            <module id="clachan">
                <h>clachan</h>
                <p><g>fuirich ann an <a href="?gd=clachan">clachan</a></g> <en>lives in a village</en> –
                    <xl>
                        <li>
                            <gd>Càit a bheil thu a’ fuireach? Tha mi a’ <m>fuireach</m> anns a’
                                chlachan.</gd>
                            <tr>Where do you live? I live in the village.</tr>
                            <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <gd>Nach robh Calum a’ fuireach anns a’ chlachan? Bha gu dearbh.</gd>
                            <tr>Wasn’t Calum living in the village? Yes, indeed he was.</tr>
                            <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <gd>An robh thu a’ fuireach anns a’ chlachan? Cha robh.</gd>
                            <tr>Were you living in the village? No, I wasn’t.</tr>
                            <ref text="617">td. 21 [229]</ref>
                        </li>
                    </xl>
                </p>
            </module>
        </section>
    </section>


